A while ago, I had the exact same error. You get this error because you forgot to remove the `https://` from your `hostName` property.

Just update the code like this:

```java
@Configuration
@Getter
@Setter
public class ESRestClient {

    private String hostName = &quot;xxxxxxx.gcp.cloud.es.io&quot;;
....
```

As you already define `https` in `new HttpHost`, it can&#39;t be in the hostname.

